{"tid":1110323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【火爆長者激戰港男】手機音量爆發衝突 長者爆粗：你咁夠薑寸我","createTime":"2019-04-16T13:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T15:36:13.000Z","uid":106310,"like":2,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"24807e50a4747f6db6ac9589ffb43fa736da27d1","tid":1110323,"uid":106310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_664797_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_664797_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=fa9192d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_664797_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA&h=0627ec93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_664797_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【火爆長者激戰港男】手機音量爆發衝突 長者爆粗：你咁夠薑寸我<br />\n<br />\n19小時前     <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有長者疑因在港鐵車廂手機聲音過大，不滿被人勸阻，口出惡言破口大罵，惹來乘客非議。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上月尾，一列港鐵行走荃灣線的車廂內，港男疑不滿長者手機聲音過大，向長者作出勸喻，豈料長者卻大動肝火，以粗言穢語連聲斥責，「我留鬍子這麼長，細路，你竟然夠薑寸我？我有三部手機，你有什麼，憑什麼寸我？正一斯文敗類，不自量力，正衰仔！」港男起初並無理會，惟長者卻罵過不停，有一名男乘客看不過眼，要求長者閉咀，亦有乘客更調座位，避之則吉。<br />\n<br />\n未幾，港男不忿被罵，以手機反拍對方，長者亦不甘示弱，忽然脫去上衣，展露瘦削的上身，繼續開火炮轟。最後港男在旺角下車前作出「挑機」，要求對方下車，氣氛充滿火藥味。<br />\n<br />\n對於長者在地鐵車廂的罵戰，市民都有各的說法。<br />\n<br />\nZoe稱會尊重長者，不想責罵對方，希望大家自覺，認為最理想方法是車長能作出調停，提醒對方小心言論。<br />\n<br />\n羅小姐有一顆敬老的心，她表示長者過去曾經是社會的棟樑，亦為社會作出貢獻，應該可享有特權，寄語年青人稍作忍讓，「不應跟他爭辯什麼，雖然最終我們有理據，但我覺得可以包容，因為我心內是敬老。但如果他行為太過份，影響小朋友，嚇壞他們，我會向他反映，否則我只會調位，以身體語言告訴他。」她認為現今年青人不太懂得敬老，但又不能指責他們錯誤，因為彼此想法感受有所不同。<br />\n<br />\n來自湖北的遊客宋先生則指，中國傳統社會敬老，長者可獲得優先待遇，他會作出包容，「畢竟是公共場合，確實是不文明行為，但某程度上，也算是他自由，他付費乘車，我也很快到達目的地，不會長時間對著他，如無法勸阻便算了。」他也冀長者能多顧及別人感受，學懂站在別人的角度思考。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解班廢老咁串?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zyQ6HP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zyQ6HP.jpg&h=4e5c5929&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d1703eff32458a9f03ca52ac43726aff80fa89","tid":1110323,"uid":62532,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"仲叫人敬老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尊敬係自己賺返黎架"},{"pid":"d1bac0c6f0779eb18b0fa7dcca1547730c50d2f7","tid":1110323,"uid":209301,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"啲受訪者都痴線嘅"},{"pid":"91409d95a3ba9c318a745b65d21363abb33d0c85","tid":1110323,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"中國傳統社會敬老<br />\n所以先有咁多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c910e17b4e1e5cabbc1f857b4ddd980d96629ef","tid":1110323,"uid":172464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:28:57.000Z","msg":"羅小姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人喺佢耳邊大大聲播大明咒"},{"pid":"0eb9baf70dbca7d9e641028108ada36742dacd01","tid":1110323,"uid":33053,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"臭閪羅小姐同Zoe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3464181739c73f5dde598b6e0ef7635b77eef667","tid":1110323,"uid":225295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"24807e50a4747f6db6ac9589ffb43fa736da27d1","tid":1110323,"uid":106310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_664797_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_664797_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=fa9192d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_664797_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA&h=0627ec93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_664797_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3IEYACk1EEleoIV0aZDENNer5-YO4KsONpOal6-pbmYoguzSXyXf7SlKA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【火爆長者激戰港男】手機音量爆發衝突 長者爆粗：你咁夠薑寸我<br />\n<br />\n19小時前     <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有長者疑因在港鐵車廂手機聲音過大，不滿被人勸阻，口出惡言破口大罵，惹來乘客非議。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上月尾，一列港鐵行走荃灣線的車廂內，港男疑不滿長者手機聲音過大，向長者作出勸喻，豈料長者卻大動肝火，以粗言穢語連聲斥責，「我留鬍子這麼長，細路，你竟然夠薑寸我？我有三部手機，你有什麼，憑什麼寸我？正一斯文敗類，不自量力，正衰仔！」港男起初並無理會，惟長者卻罵過不停，有一名男乘客看不過眼，要求長者閉咀，亦有乘客更調座位，避之則吉。<br />\n<br />\n未幾